titleInfo.title: USA v. Larose
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER - LaRose's motion to continue trial (Filing No. 19) is granted. Trial of this matter is re-scheduled for July 2, 2012, before Judge Joseph F. Bataillon and a jury. The ends of justice have been served by granting such motion and outweigh the interests of the public and the defendant in a speedy trial. The additional time arising as a result of the granting of the motion, i.e., the time between May 18, 2012, and July 2, 2012, shall be deemed excludable time in any computation of time under the requirement of the Speedy Trial Act as to Leslie A. Larose (1). Ordered by Magistrate Judge Thomas D. Thalken. (AOA)
